{"tid":15620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"福建地盤挖出疑似古幣　民眾瘋搶一夜掃光","createTime":"2016-12-01T05:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T12:34:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aec5818ce1b1d8c86aa655196b462ac63b86ad1b","tid":15620,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161201/photo/bkncn-20161201033242201-1201_05011_001_01p.jpg?20161201035130\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161201%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161201033242201-1201_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161201035130&h=394434c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n福建漳州市南江濱路一個地盤，前日挖出百多枚疑似清代與民國的錢幣，而消息傳出後更惹來大批民眾瘋搶，目前已所剩無幾。當地記者得悉事件後已報警求助，阻止民眾哄搶，目前警方正對事件作進一步調查。 <br />\n<br />\n有漳州市民表示，該些錢幣前日被地盤一名挖掘機司機發現，粗略估計有百多枚。惟消息傳出後，民眾即帶同鋤頭等工具到地盤挖掘，將一枚又一枚的錢幣拿回家，未有人阻止。 <br />\n<br />\n從幾張錢幣的照片可見，其中一些刻上「康熙通寶」的字樣。而個別錢幣則刻上「中華民國」的字樣，相信是民國期間的錢幣，惟真假仍待專家確認。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161201/photo/bkncn-20161201033242201-1201_05011_001_03b.jpg?20161201035130\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161201%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161201033242201-1201_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20161201035130&h=0c9bad6c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n錢幣刻上「中華民國」的字樣。（互聯網圖片） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161201/photo/bkncn-20161201033242201-1201_05011_001_04b.jpg?20161201035130\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161201%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161201033242201-1201_05011_001_04b.jpg%3F20161201035130&h=3d839a1b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n錢幣刻上「康熙通寶」的字樣。（互聯網圖片）"},{"pid":"fa92dee85f53c12755d9d7d400690171183e24d8","tid":15620,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"反了"},{"pid":"0c8853e2870e5dc898462ee0b31a4bbd6b18aeba","tid":15620,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"蝗"},{"pid":"db4490d72590f0b5ef6fab8b6ef331fd40e13277","tid":15620,"uid":34511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:32:24.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"943aa45ad981e10f46fc96218703645df9d6267e","tid":15620,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9f2290e72c12e5c3c653a5f5a70c6e2bdac206","tid":15620,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:25:41.000Z","msg":"如果係香港都會有一堆人搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw中國來，正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f4ed7506a429c09b845d337146260168229f94","tid":15620,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:26:28.000Z","msg":"好兆呀！<br />\n<br />\n中華民國再來了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0b62087b9cfe4a7a2aee824485d7c9fbdabea0","tid":15620,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"民國硬幣好似係銀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1072241553355b6fbc77f8f866a2618b696260","tid":15620,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係香港都會有一堆人搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw中國來，正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n家陣走入人地地盤搶喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係蝗國先做得出"}]}